## 9. Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------|-----|
| `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'evals'` | PYTHONPATH not set | Run with `PYTHONPATH=.` prefix |
| `ERROR: Cannot find sample directory` | Wrong working directory or missing data | Use `--sample-dir /absolute/path/to/data/{sample_dir}` |
| `ERROR: Cannot find ground_truth.json` | Wrong working directory | Use `--ground-truth /absolute/path/to/ground_truth.json` |
| Sidecar `.txt` missing for a case | Extraction script wasn't re-run | Run `extract_data_text.py --data-dir ...` |
| Normalization mismatch in report | Ground truth differs from extracted in formatting only | Expected — normalizer handles this. "MATCH" means they match after normalization |

